preference.name: CATIA_manage_designtables
preference.preference_description: Defines how Design Tables are managed. - Design Tables are managed in all processes (TRUE) - Design Tables are not managed in any processes (FALSE) - Design Tables are only managed during the Load, Export, Export Spreadsheet processes and not in the Save, Import, Import Spreadsheet, State Details and Check-in/Check-out processes (LOAD_NOSAVE) - Design Tables are only managed during the Load, Export, Export processes and a provide a prompt to manage Design Tables in the Save, Import, Import Spreadsheet, State Details and Check-in/Check-out processes (LOAD_SAVEDISPLAY)
